Issue Assessment:
- Identify remote access method (VPN, RDP, Citrix, VDI)
- Determine error message or connection behavior
- Verify user is authorized for remote access
- Check if issue is user-specific or affecting multiple users

{% if access_type == 'vpn' %}
VPN Troubleshooting:
- Verify VPN client is installed and up to date
- Check VPN gateway status
- Verify user credentials are correct
- Test MFA is completing successfully
- Check internet connectivity before VPN
- Try alternate VPN server/gateway
- Review VPN client logs for errors
- Check split tunnel vs full tunnel configuration
- Verify no conflicting VPN clients
- Reinstall VPN client if persistent issues
{% endif %}

{% if access_type == 'rdp' %}
Remote Desktop Troubleshooting:
- Verify target computer is powered on
- Check Remote Desktop is enabled on target
- Verify user has RDP access permissions
- Check Network Level Authentication settings
- Test network connectivity to target (ping)
- Verify firewall allows RDP (port 3389)
- Check for RDP session limits
- Test with IP address vs hostname
{% endif %}

{% if access_type == 'citrix' %}
Citrix Troubleshooting:
- Verify Citrix Workspace app is installed
- Check Citrix gateway/StoreFront status
- Clear Citrix Workspace cache
- Verify user has published app/desktop access
- Test with web-based access (Citrix Web)
- Check for Citrix Receiver version issues
- Review Citrix Director for session info
{% endif %}

{% if access_type == 'vdi' %}
VDI Troubleshooting:
- Verify VDI platform status
- Check user's desktop pool assignment
- Verify available capacity in pool
- Review connection broker logs
- Test alternate connection method
- Check display protocol settings
{% endif %}

Network and Connectivity:
- Verify home internet is working
- Test speed and latency
- Check for firewall or ISP blocks
- Try from different network if possible

Authentication:
- Verify password is current
- Check MFA enrollment and device
- Look for account lockout
- Review conditional access policies

Resolution:
- Confirm remote access is working
- Document troubleshooting steps taken
- Provide user with remote access guide
- Note any configuration changes made
